articles.title: UK’s Starmer in Kyiv for security talks with a pledge for a ‘100-year partnership’ with Ukraine - The Associated Press
articles.description: U.K. Prime Minister Keir Starmer and Ukrainian President Volodymyr Zelenskyy have signed a 100-year partnership agreement. It's part of a European show of support to continue helping Ukraine prevail in its nearly three-year war with Russia. The announcement o…
